  "prompt": "What are some suggested heart touching (English) love songs?",
  "response": "Here\u2019s a list of heart-touching English love songs that evoke deep emotions and resonate with themes of love, longing, and connection:\n\n### Classic Love Songs:\n1. **\"Your Song\" - Elton John**  \n   A timeless ballad expressing pure, heartfelt love.\n   \n2. **\"Wonderful Tonight\" - Eric Clapton**  \n   A tender song about appreciating a loved one in a quiet, intimate moment.\n\n3. **\"Something\" - The Beatles**  \n   George Harrison\u2019s beautiful ode to love and admiration.\n\n4. **\"Make You Feel My Love\" - Bob Dylan (or Adele\u2019s cover)**  \n   A heartfelt declaration of unwavering love.\n\n5. **\"Unchained Melody\" - The Righteous Brothers**  \n   A powerful and emotional classic about longing and love.\n\n### Modern Love Songs:\n6. **\"All of Me\" - John Legend**  \n   A soulful ballad celebrating love in its entirety, flaws and all.\n\n7. **\"Thinking Out Loud\" - Ed Sheeran**  \n   A romantic promise of lifelong love and devotion.\n\n8. **\"A Thousand Years\" - Christina Perri**  \n   A heartfelt song about enduring love, often associated with weddings.\n\n9. **\"Perfect\" - Ed Sheeran**  \n   A sweet and dreamy song about finding the perfect love.\n\n10. **\"You Are the Reason\" - Calum Scott & Leona Lewis**  \n    A moving duet about how love is the reason for everything.\n\n### Emotional and Poignant:\n11. **\"I Will Always Love You\" - Whitney Houston (originally by Dolly Parton)**  \n    A powerful declaration of everlasting love and letting go.\n\n12. **\"My Heart Will Go On\" - Celine Dion**  \n    The iconic theme from *Titanic*, a tribute to eternal love.\n\n13. **\"I Can\u2019t Help Falling in Love\" - Elvis Presley (or covers by artists like Haley Reinhart)**  \n    A tender and classic love song about falling deeply in love.\n\n14. **\"Fix You\" - Coldplay**  \n    A comforting song about being there for someone you love through tough times.\n\n15. **\"Hallelujah\" - Leonard Cohen (or Jeff Buckley\u2019s cover)**  \n    A poetic and emotional song that often resonates with themes of love and longing.\n\n### Soulful and Deep:\n16. **\"Let It Be Me\" - Ray LaMontagne**  \n    A soulful ballad about offering unconditional love and support.\n\n17. **\"Stay With Me\" - Sam Smith**  \n    A heartfelt plea for love and companionship.\n\n18. **\"Say You Won\u2019t Let Go\" - James Arthur**  \n    A touching song about cherishing a lifelong partner.\n\n19. **\"Better Together\" - Jack Johnson**  \n    A warm and soothing song about how love feels complete when together.\n\n20. **\"You and Me\" - Lifehouse**  \n    A song about the simplicity and beauty of being in love.\n\nThese songs span different eras and styles but share the common thread of touching the heart with their heartfelt lyrics and melodies.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
